---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Visit Our Farm Stand - String Prairie Gardens & Barefoot Flower Farm"
  description="Discover our hidden gem farm stand on St. Mary's Road, outdoor nursery, greenhouse, and gorgeous event venue with incredible valley views."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/Images/farm-stand-exterior.jpeg" alt="Farm stand exterior" />
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>A Hidden Gem Worth Discovering</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        You don't need to "go to town" for beautiful plants and flowers!
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <p class="lead-text">
          This is a hidden gem that deserves more wide-spread awareness. String
          Prairie Gardens & Barefoot Flower Farm offers a unique destination for
          plant lovers, flower enthusiasts, and anyone seeking a peaceful escape
          into nature's beauty.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="locations-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Two Locations to Explore</h2>

      <div class="location-card">
        <div class="location-image">
          <img
            src="/Images/nursery-stand-potted-flowers.jpeg"
            alt="Farm stand with potted flowers"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="location-content">
          <div class="location-badge">Location 1</div>
          <h3>The Farm Stand</h3>
          <p class="location-address">Located on St. Mary's Road</p>
          <p>
            Start your journey at our precious farm stand, packed with beautiful
            plants and flowers. This charming roadside stop offers a curated
            selection of our freshest blooms and healthiest plants. It's the
            perfect place to pick up a quick bouquet, find a new houseplant, or
            discover seasonal favorites.
          </p>
          <ul class="location-features">
            <li>Fresh-cut flowers daily</li>
            <li>Potted plants and succulents</li>
            <li>Seasonal specialties</li>
            <li>Easy roadside access</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="directions-callout">
        <div class="directions-icon">üîµ</div>
        <div class="directions-text">
          <h4>Follow the Blue Arrows!</h4>
          <p>
            Turn right onto McReynolds Road and follow the little blue arrows
            painted on the road. A five-minute scenic drive will bring you to
            our main nursery and event venue.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="location-card reverse">
        <div class="location-image">
          <img
            src="/Images/farm-grounds-garden-arches.jpeg"
            alt="Nursery grounds with garden arches"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="location-content">
          <div class="location-badge">Location 2</div>
          <h3>The Nursery & Event Venue</h3>
          <p class="location-address">440 McReynolds Rd, Rosanky, TX 78953</p>
          <p>
            Our main property features a large outdoor nursery and greenhouse
            where you'll find an incredible selection of plants. But that's not
            all‚Äîdiscover our gorgeous event home with an incredible view over
            the valley, perfect for weddings, parties, and special celebrations.
          </p>
          <ul class="location-features">
            <li>Large outdoor nursery</li>
            <li>Climate-controlled greenhouse</li>
            <li>Event venue with valley views</li>
            <li>Wedding and party hosting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Everything You Need</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        String Prairie Gardens & Barefoot Flower Farm has everything you need
        for your garden, home, or special occasion
      </p>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">üå±</div>
          <h3>Garden Updates</h3>
          <p>
            Refresh your garden or flowerbeds with our wide selection of
            annuals, perennials, native plants, and ornamental shrubs. Our
            expert team can help you choose the perfect plants for your Texas
            landscape.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">üè°</div>
          <h3>New Home Setup</h3>
          <p>
            Setting up a new home? We have everything from foundational
            landscaping plants to indoor houseplants that bring life and color
            to every room. Make your new house feel like home with living
            greenery.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">üéÅ</div>
          <h3>Perfect Gifts</h3>
          <p>
            Find the perfect gift for the nature-lover in your life. From living
            plants to fresh bouquets, potted arrangements to gardening supplies,
            we have thoughtful gifts for every occasion and every budget.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card featured">
          <div class="service-icon">üíê</div>
          <h3>Bouquet Subscription</h3>
          <p>
            Enjoy fresh flowers every month! Our bouquet subscription service
            delivers beautiful, seasonal arrangements to you or someone you
            love. Available for local delivery‚Äîthe gift that keeps on giving!
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">üíí</div>
          <h3>Weddings & Events</h3>
          <p>
            Our stunning venue with incredible valley views is perfect for
            weddings, parties, and special events. We also provide custom flower
            arrangements for all types of celebrations.
          </p>
          <a href="/weddings" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">üå∏</div>
          <h3>Custom Arrangements</h3>
          <p>
            Need flowers for a special event? We create custom arrangements for
            weddings, anniversaries, corporate events, and more. Every
            arrangement is handcrafted with care using our freshest blooms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="gallery-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Experience the Beauty</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <img
        src="/Images/rustic-garden-shed-display.jpeg"
        alt="Rustic garden shed with flowers"
      />
      <img
        src="/Images/wedding-centerpiece-hydrangea-celosia.jpeg"
        alt="Wedding centerpiece"
      />
      <img
        src="/Images/farmers-market-bouquets-buckets.jpeg"
        alt="Fresh bouquets ready for market"
      />
      <img
        src="/Images/fall-pumpkin-floral-arrangements.jpeg"
        alt="Seasonal fall arrangements"
      />
      <img
        src="/Images/hyacinth-bulbs-cowboy-boots.jpeg"
        alt="Texas style flower display"
      />
      <img
        src="/Images/bells-of-ireland-orange-flowers-pitcher.jpeg"
        alt="Beautiful arrangement"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Come Visit Us!</h2>
        <p>
          Whether you're looking for a single plant, planning a wedding, or want
          to set up a monthly bouquet subscription, we're here to help.
          Experience the beauty of our hidden gem for yourself!
        </p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Directions</a>
          <a href="/products" class="btn btn-secondary">Shop Our Products</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-md);
    text-align: center;
    min-height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hero-bg::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(196, 132, 108, 0.85) 0%,
      rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.9) 100%
    );
  }

  .page-hero .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .intro-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .intro-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-earth);
  }

  .locations-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }

  .locations-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .location-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .location-card.reverse {
    direction: rtl;
  }

  .location-card.reverse > * {
    direction: ltr;
  }

  .location-image {
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 400px;
  }

  .location-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .location-content {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .location-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-sage);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-xs) var(--spacing-sm);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .location-content h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .location-address {
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .location-content p {
    color: var(--color-earth);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .location-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .location-features li {
    padding: var(--spacing-xs) 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-earth);
  }

  .location-features li::before {
    content: "‚úì";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-sage);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .directions-callout {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--color-blush) 0%,
      var(--color-cream) 100%
    );
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .directions-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .directions-text h4 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-xs);
    color: var(--color-sage-dark);
  }

  .directions-text p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-earth);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .services-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .services-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-earth);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(125, 148, 113, 0.15);
  }

  .service-card.featured {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--color-sage) 0%,
      var(--color-sage-dark) 100%
    );
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .service-card.featured h3 {
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .service-card.featured p {
    color: rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.9);
  }

  .service-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--color-earth);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .service-card .btn {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .gallery-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }

  .gallery-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .gallery-grid img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 250px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .gallery-grid img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .cta-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-blush);
  }

  .cta-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: var(--color-earth);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .location-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .location-card.reverse {
      direction: ltr;
    }

    .location-image {
      min-height: 250px;
    }

    .directions-callout {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .gallery-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .gallery-grid img {
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
